TI  - The Synergy between Artificial Intelligence, Remote Sensing, and Archaeological Fieldwork Validation
AU  - Canedo, D
AU  - Hipólito, J
AU  - Fonte, J
AU  - Dias, R
AU  - do Pereiro, T
